                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2950" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0269</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8819 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">驰之以恒，以薪触动 ——XH奔驰4S店化解销售顾问流失之困</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Take it as it is, touch it with income——XH Benz 4S shop to defuse the drain of sales consultants</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">许广永，桑林颖</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安徽财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">XH奔驰4S店</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">汽车销售顾问；员工流失；薪酬优化</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">automobile sales consultant, staff loss, income optimization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在人力资源管理中，薪酬管理是企业吸引人才和保留人才的重要手段之一，它既和员工切身利益先关，也关系到企业的经济效益。中国乘用车市场发展迅速，竞争愈加激烈，作为目前乘用车销售主要形态的4S店，优秀的销售队伍对于它们经营业绩的保持和提升非常关键。怎样的薪酬管理及方案才能保留销售人才，并激发他们的工作积极性，是各4S店急需解决的问题之一。XH奔驰4S店2013年成立，是国家工商局指定的小轿车经营单位、安徽省内第三家奔驰品牌授权经销商。近几年业绩虽有提升，但由于销售顾问离职率较高，对公司持续发展产生了不小的负面影响。经过调查和访谈发现，销售顾问的高离职率与公司现行的薪酬方案有很大关系。公司王总亲自过问，责成人力资源部具体负责销售顾问薪酬方案的改善和优化，以实现稳定销售顾问队伍和公司稳步发展的目标。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Compensation management is an important means for enterprises to attract talents and remain talents in human resource management. It is not only important to the interests of staffs, but also the development of the company. Through the rationally use compensation plan, it can motivate employees to create the biggest value for the enterprise. The increasing of competition inside passenger car industry and function of car sales staff to promote enterprise development. Automobile enterprises highlight the importance of talent strategy. In the face of increasingly fierce market competition, automobile manufacturers will expand their sales network and improve the brand market share through increasing new 4S shops. In the existing environment, what kind of salary plans make the sales department to play the largest, that is the most concerned issues for the human resources department of each 4S shops. this case mainly refers to Bengbu Star Benz 4S shops compensation design and turnover rate as a theme for case study, through its sales consultant high turnover of events and issues in the rapid development, analysis compensation design knowledge structure and the key points, which discuss during the process of rapid development, how to timely optimize the design of the compensation, reduce sales consultant turnover rate and improve their working enthusiasm and efficiency, provide reference and lessons for enterprise&#39;s stable sales team and steady development.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2016</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">薪酬管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017-10</td>
                            </tr>
